</ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>toLocaleString()</strong></code> 方法返回一个该对象的字符串表示。此方法被用于派生对象为了特定语言环境的目的（locale-specific purposes）而重载使用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>obj</var>.toLocaleString();</code>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>表示对象的字符串。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a> <code>toLocaleString</code> 返回调用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a> 的结果。</p>\n\n<p>该函数提供给对象一个通用的<code>toLocaleString</code>&nbsp;方法，即使不是全部都可以使用它。 见下面的列表。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"覆盖_tolocalestring_的对象","title":"覆盖&nbsp;<code>toLocaleString</code> 的对象","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/toLocaleString\"><code>Array.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a>：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/toLocaleString\"><code>Number.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a>：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toLocaleString\"><code>Date.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"覆盖 toLocaleString 的对象"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\"